</div> <div id="Common-Names" class="Common-Names">
<p class="Common-Names"><b>Common names:</b> Chiretta, Chuan xin lian, Kalmegh, Kirata</p>
</div> <div id="Botanical-Names" class="Botanical-Names">
<p class="Botanical-Names"><b>Botanical name:</b> <em>Andrographis paniculata</em></p>
</div> <div id="Photo" class="Photo"><img src="http://healthnotes.info/http/ltd/images/Herb/Andrographis.jpg" align="right" height=
"200" width="200" alt="Photo">
<p class="Photo-Credit">&#169;&nbsp;Martin Wall</p>
</div> <div id="Sidebar-Display" class="Sidebar-Main-Column">
