</div> <div id="Botany" class="Botany">
<h3 class="Botany-Heading">Parts used and where grown</h3>
<p>Andrographis originated in the plains of India, and it also grows in China. The leaves and
flowers are used medicinally.</p>
</div> <div id="Condition-Summary" class="Condition-Summary">
<p id="Condition-Summary-Heading" class="Condition-Summary-Heading">Andrographis has been used
in connection with the following conditions <span class="Qualifier">(refer to the individual
health concern for complete information)</span>:</p>
